          <title>Matteo Berrettini gives Italy a 1-0 lead over the Netherlands in the Davis Cup final</title>
          <description><![CDATA[MALAGA, Spain (AP) — Matteo Berrettini put Italy ahead 1-0 against the Netherlands in the final of the Davis Cup on Sunday by beating Botic van de Zandschulp 6-4, 6-2, setting up No. 1-ranked Jannik Sinner for a chance to clinch the country's second consecutive championship in the team competition.]]></description>
